name: Homage to Sophie Taeuber-Arp (Aubette Composition) #1
description:
First in a series of pieces based on the work of Swiss Dada and Constructivist artist, Sophie Taeuber-Arp.

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sophie_Taeuber-Arp

This is a generative work based on her Aubette compositions (1927-28).

Edition of 20.
